tence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 890, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Clickhereto buy\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She managed to, in her own words, \\\"get it together\\\" in time for the bronze medal playoff where she beat Anna Karolina Schmiedlova 6-2 6-1 to claim her first Olympic medal.\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 1063, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her own words\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 924}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 951}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze medal playoff\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 980}, {\"ngram\": \"Anna Karolina Schmiedlova\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"her first Olympic medal\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1062}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the victory, the 23-year-old explained just how emotional she was before forcing herself to turn it around.\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1177, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the victory\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You do not wanna know,\\\" Swiatek laughed when asked how she spent the last 24 hours.\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1263, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Swiatek\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"the last 24 hours\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Well truth be told, I do not remember, maybe I cried like that after losing in Australia after I won my first Grand Slam.\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1344, \"end\": 1353, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9209108204231303, \"rank\": 0.06108852033230423, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"truth\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1275}, {\"ngram\": \"my first Grand Slam\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After Roland Garros that was in October and then we started the season in Australia, I lost and I cried for like three days basically.\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1521, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1393, \"end\": 1406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 0.9999999996521183, \"rank\": 3.477605446517471e-10, \"text\": \"Roland Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}, {\"begin\": 1461, \"end\": 1470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9209108204231303, \"rank\": 0.06108852033230423, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"October\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"the season\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1457}, {\"ngram\": \"three days\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1510}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think if I wasn't playing today I would cry [for] over a week.\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1586, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a week\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I needed to get it together.\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1618, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I probably cried for like six hours yesterday.\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"six hours\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was really tough.\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1688, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know, sometimes it feels like it's sport and it's tennis and usually I am able to have the distance to all of it and just understand that it's only one part of my life but this time it was like somebody really broke my heart, you know?\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1933, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1738}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1754}, {\"ngram\": \"the distance\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1797}, {\"ngram\": \"only one part\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1854}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1865}, {\"ngram\": \"somebody\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"my heart\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's crazy, honestly.\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1958, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But the five-time Grand Slam champion will use her Olympics experience as a lesson to be learned.\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 2057, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the five-time Grand Slam champion\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 1997}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympics experience\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2030}, {\"ngram\": \"a lesson\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She continued: \\\"Because of the fact that I happened, I know I still have so much work to do to understand myself and what's happening to me sometimes a little bit better.\", \"from\": 2058, \"to\": 2228, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2093}, {\"ngram\": \"so much work\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Because of the fact that I am No.\", \"from\": 2229, \"to\": 2262, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"1 for such a long time and I won so many tournaments, I literally felt that I can handle everything, you know?\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2373, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a long time\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2285}, {\"ngram\": \"so many tournaments\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2315}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2477, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our community members\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2396}, {\"ngram\": \"special offers\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2426}, {\"ngram\": \"promotions\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2438}, {\"ngram\": \"adverts\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2451}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2459}, {\"ngram\": \"our partners\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2508, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any time\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy \\\"And this tournament showed me that's still not the case.\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2592, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2531}, {\"ngram\": \"this tournament\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2552}, {\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 2580, \"to\": 2588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So actually, I was maybe a little bit too arrogant with myself because I thought that I have handled so much pressure before that I think I am going to handle this one as well.\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2769, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so much pressure\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2710}, {\"ngram\": \"this one\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2760}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And now I am motivated to work even harder and I think I am going to have a bit more humility with everything so I think this actually can end up with me working better in the future.\\\"\", \"from\": 2770, \"to\": 2954, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bit more humility\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2863}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2869, \"to\": 2879}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 2952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not the first time that Swiatek has struggled at the Olympics - she was also in tears when she lost in the second round in Tokyo three years ago.\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 3106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3084, \"end\": 3089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9997092230015014, \"rank\": 0.000290267421506259, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 2979}, {\"ngram\": \"Swiatek\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 2992}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3010, \"to\": 3022}, {\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3046}, {\"ngram\": \"the second round\", \"from\": 3064, \"to\": 3080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after her semi-final match against Zheng - which she branded \\\"one of the toughest losses I probably ever had in my career\\\" - she realised the extent of her struggles at the Games.\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3146, \"end\": 3151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.1391126364225396e-12, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her semi-final match\", \"from\": 3117, \"to\": 3137}, {\"ngram\": \"the toughest losses\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3199}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3232}, {\"ngram\": \"the extent\", \"from\": 3249, \"to\": 3259}, {\"ngram\": \"her struggles\", \"from\": 3263, \"to\": 3276}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3280, \"to\": 3289}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Honestly, during the competition, I wasn't really aware that it was so much because I understood that I was stressed and I accepted that it was going to be that way.\", \"from\": 3292, \"to\": 3458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 3310, \"to\": 3325}, {\"ngram\": \"that way\", \"from\": 3449, \"to\": 3457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was in Tokyo and I saw how hard it is and how different this tournament is than what I had on tour.\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3468, \"end\": 3473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9997092230015014, \"rank\": 0.000290267421506259, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this tournament\", \"from\": 3517, \"to\": 3532}, {\"ngram\": \"tour\", \"from\": 3555, \"to\": 3559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think [the issue was] playing these few matches in a row without having a little bit of time to not really think about tennis, which I am more used to now when we have longer 1000 tournaments and Grand Slams,\\\" she explained.\", \"from\": 3561, \"to\": 3787, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the issue\", \"from\": 3570, \"to\": 3579}, {\"ngram\": \"these few matches\", \"from\": 3593, \"to\": 3610}, {\"ngram\": \"a row\", \"from\": 3614, \"to\": 3619}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 3635, \"to\": 3647}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3651, \"to\": 3655}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis\", \"from\": 3682, \"to\": 3688}, {\"ngram\": \"longer 1000 tournaments\", \"from\": 3731, \"to\": 3754}, {\"ngram\": \"Grand Slams\", \"from\": 3759, \"to\": 3770}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This plus the fact that I actually realised yesterday that I wasn't really playing for myself, I was more playing for everybody else, for the country, for my team, for everybody that hoped that I am going to win a medal and probably win a gold medal.\", \"from\": 3789, \"to\": 4040, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 3908, \"to\": 3917}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 3928, \"to\": 3939}, {\"ngram\": \"my team\", \"from\": 3945, \"to\": 3952}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 3958, \"to\": 3967}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 4002, \"to\": 4009}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 4027, \"to\": 4039}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think I talked about it, I tried to work through it but I wasn't quite aware of how deep it was in me and how much of a baggage that was.\", \"from\": 4041, \"to\": 4180, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a baggage\", \"from\": 4161, \"to\": 4170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I only realised that after I lost and honestly I know I have not been playing my A-game here probably, I wasn't feeling like I can move really naturally and in a way that I am used to, especially on clay.\\\"\", \"from\": 4181, \"to\": 4389, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my A-game\", \"from\": 4262, \"to\": 4271}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 4344, \"to\": 4349}, {\"ngram\": \"clay\", \"from\": 4383, \"to\": 4387}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Carlos Alcaraz thrashes Auger-Aliassime as Spaniard one win from Olympic gold Do not miss:Andrey Rublev deletes controversial Khelif post after Russian sparked backlash Do not miss:Novak Djokovic shows true colours with message to Andy Murray after retirement We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 4391, \"to\": 4775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4403, \"end\": 4417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 4494, \"end\": 4507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrey_Rublev\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrey Rublev\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"],