es based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 4776, \"to\": 4852, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"adverts\", \"from\": 4793, \"to\": 4800}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4806, \"to\": 4808}, {\"ngram\": \"3rd parties\", \"from\": 4813, \"to\": 4824}, {\"ngram\": \"our understanding\", \"from\": 4834, \"to\": 4851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 4853, \"to\": 4885, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any time\", \"from\": 4876, \"to\": 4884}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy Although she bounced back for the bronze medal playoff, Swiatek confessed that she was still feeling mixed emotions when she sat on her bench after beating Schmiedlova.\", \"from\": 4886, \"to\": 5080, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 4891, \"to\": 4908}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze medal playoff\", \"from\": 4939, \"to\": 4963}, {\"ngram\": \"Swiatek\", \"from\": 4965, \"to\": 4972}, {\"ngram\": \"mixed emotions\", \"from\": 5010, \"to\": 5024}, {\"ngram\": \"her bench\", \"from\": 5041, \"to\": 5050}, {\"ngram\": \"Schmiedlova\", \"from\": 5065, \"to\": 5076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"When I sat down after the match I was really confused because I still feel like I lost yesterday and it was a huge loss but on the other hand I won today and it was tough as well so I should be proud of that.\", \"from\": 5081, \"to\": 5300, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the match\", \"from\": 5114, \"to\": 5123}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge loss\", \"from\": 5200, \"to\": 5211}, {\"ngram\": \"the other hand\", \"from\": 5219, \"to\": 5233}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a lot of mixed emotions and still is.\", \"from\": 5302, \"to\": 5349, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 5312, \"to\": 5317}, {\"ngram\": \"mixed emotions\", \"from\": 5321, \"to\": 5335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think I am going to have a few days of negative emotions from yesterday and then they are going to pass and I am going to remember winning the bronze medal - I hope so, I guess.\\\"\", \"from\": 5350, \"to\": 5530, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few days\", \"from\": 5377, \"to\": 5387}, {\"ngram\": \"negative emotions\", \"from\": 5391, \"to\": 5408}, {\"ngram\": \"yesterday\", \"from\": 5414, \"to\": 5423}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze medal\", \"from\": 5491, \"to\": 5507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Swiatek tries to learn how to cope better with the pressure, she will be using one of her fellow young Grand Slam champions as an example.\", \"from\": 5532, \"to\": 5673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Swiatek\", \"from\": 5535, \"to\": 5542}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 5582, \"to\": 5594}, {\"ngram\": \"her fellow young Grand Slam champions\", \"from\": 5621, \"to\": 5658}, {\"ngram\": \"an example\", \"from\": 5662, \"to\": 5672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I actually am watchingCarlos Alcarazand I can see he's enjoying every minute of it and he's a great example actually of how to handle all of that well,\\\" she smiled.\", \"from\": 5674, \"to\": 5839, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"watchingCarlos\", \"from\": 5689, \"to\": 5703}, {\"ngram\": \"every minute\", \"from\": 5739, \"to\": 5751}, {\"ngram\": \"a great example\", \"from\": 5767, \"to\": 5782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH CONNECT WITH US TODAY'S PAPER See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 5841, \"to\": 6010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5978, \"end\": 5991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6972471726829604e-26, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\